    </p>
    <p>
      📩 if you're interested in getting in touch, feel free to reach out in my
      e-mail <code class="text-amber-700 cursor-pointer" data-copy-button
        >brunettoyuri@gmail.com</code
      >
       or via my socials, you can find me anywhere using <code
        class="text-amber-700 cursor-pointer"
        data-copy-button>@brun3tto</code
